      <title>亿万富翁乔·刘易斯在内幕交易案中认罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/billionaire-joe-lewis-to-plead-guilty-in-insider-trading-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国亿万富翁乔·刘易斯 (Joe Lewis) 将承认向他的私人飞行员和女友传递内幕信息，这给这位 86 岁的投资者从伦敦东区一跃成为英国最富有的人之一的辉煌历程蒙上了污点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/billionaire-joe-lewis-to-plead-guilty-in-insider-trading-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 14:49:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
