      <title>尽管整体数据意外上升，墨西哥一月初核心通胀仍放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/mexico-headline-inflation-unexpectedly-sped-up-in-early-january</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥的总体通胀在今年前两周出人意料地加速，而受到密切关注的核心指标则放缓，因为央行行长表示他们将讨论最终开始降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/mexico-headline-inflation-unexpectedly-sped-up-in-early-january</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 12:11:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
